" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Muc-Off has teamed up with Trash Free Trails for the #BadtoRad Christmas Campaign. The initiative looks to encourage riders to pick up any litter at their local riding spot in a bid to keep our forests, moors and waterways free of trash.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails.jpg\" alt=\"mucoff badtorad litter pickup trashfreetrails win frame strap\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/16042256/mucoff-badtorad-christmas-litter-pick-up-trash-free-trails-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>It’s easy to get involved: simply head out to the trails and pick up as much trash as you can possibly find, then post your findings on Instagram or TikTok with the hashtag #BadtoRad for a chance to win one of ten <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/gear-roundup-packs-straps-from-mission-workshop-muc-off-plus-eco-friendly-reflective-packs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Muc-Off Frame Strap and Dry Bag Bundles</a>.</p><h2>Muc-Off #BadtoRad Christmas Campaign</h2><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/25qvoIyW10g?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><div id=\"attachment_279086\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-279086\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag.jpg\" alt=\"muc-off frame strap waterproof bag\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/23041939/muc-off-waterproof-cargo-bag-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-279086\">Aforementioned swag up for grabs…</p></div><p><a href=\"https://muc-off.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Muc-Off.com</em></a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.tr